column5: First Day of muskie fishing for me this year........
Great way to start Larry!!!!  I saw one today.. followed for the full oval at boat side.. that'll keep me smilin for now!
Nice Ski Dude !!! I gotta get me one a those
nice work!   I am going to head out this morning to try for my first ever, I'll be happy with one half that size  -AA
great way to start a season! congrats
Nice start to the season she sure is clean
Nice fish! I went out without any success on Saturday. I must have only made 999 casts, cause i didnt catch anything...lol
Is it lungelarry cause you name is Larry or cause you fish the Larry?(st.lawrence) cause that looks like a st.Lawrence ski to me...  Nice fish
WOW, what a healthy looking fish.
wow what a tank, nice fish
Nice clean looking fish .......good one Larry!!
Beautiful fish...super clean!  I got a 46 on Saturday that looked like it went thru a meat grinder from the spawn!!    Nice!
